---
export const prerender = true;
import Shop from '@/layouts/Shop.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@/components/astro/Breadcrumb.astro';
import { tenant } from '@/config/tenant';
---

<Shop
  title={`FAQ | ${tenant.name}`}
  description="Frequently asked questions about nicotine pouches, shipping, returns, age verification, and ordering from SnusFriend."
>
  <section class="bg-background text-foreground">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'FAQ' }]} />

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Everything you need to know about ordering from {tenant.name}. Can't find your
        answer? <a href="/contact" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Contact us</a>.
      </p>

      <!-- Nicotine Pouches -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Nicotine Pouches</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What are nicotine pouches?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Nicotine pouches are small, tobacco-free pouches that you place between your
            gum and upper lip. They deliver nicotine through the oral mucosa without smoke,
            vapour, or tobacco leaf. Each pouch lasts roughly 20-40 minutes depending on
            the brand and strength.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How do I choose the right strength?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Nicotine strengths typically range from 2 mg to 20 mg per pouch. If you are new
            to nicotine pouches, start with a low strength (2-6 mg) and work your way up.
            Experienced users often prefer 8-12 mg for regular use. Ultra-strong products
            (14 mg+) are best suited for heavy users transitioning from smoking or other
            tobacco products.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Are nicotine pouches safer than smoking?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Nicotine pouches do not involve combustion or tobacco leaf, which eliminates
            exposure to tar and many harmful chemicals found in cigarette smoke. While
            nicotine itself is addictive, public health agencies generally consider
            tobacco-free nicotine products a lower-risk alternative to smoking. Always
            consult your doctor if you have health concerns.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How many pouches come in a can?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Most cans contain 20 pouches, though some brands offer 15 or 24. The product
            page always lists the exact count. Multi-pack rolls (typically 10 cans) are
            available for popular products at a discounted per-can price.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Product Questions -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Product Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How long does a nicotine pouch last?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            A single nicotine pouch typically lasts <strong>20 to 40 minutes</strong>. Flavour
            peaks around the 5-10 minute mark, while nicotine absorbs steadily throughout.
            Mini pouches tend toward the shorter end (~20 min), while slim pouches last longer
            (~30-40 min). Remove the pouch when the flavour fades. Read our full guide on
            <a href="/blog/how-long-do-nicotine-pouches-last" class="underline hover:text-foreground">how long nicotine pouches last</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What is the difference between nicotine pouches and snus?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            The key difference is tobacco. <strong>Snus contains ground tobacco leaf</strong>,
            while nicotine pouches are completely tobacco-free — using pharmaceutical-grade
            nicotine with plant fibres instead. Nicotine pouches are white (no staining), don't
            need refrigeration, and are legal across the EU. Snus is only legally sold in Sweden.
            Read our full <a href="/blog/nicotine-pouches-vs-snus" class="underline hover:text-foreground">nicotine pouches vs snus comparison</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What are the side effects of nicotine pouches?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Common side effects include mild tingling under the lip, occasional hiccups, and
            in some cases nausea or dizziness. These are almost always caused by using a
            <strong>strength that's too high</strong> for your tolerance. The solution: try a
            lower mg pouch. Start with 2-4 mg if you're new.
            See our <a href="/blog/nicotine-pouch-side-effects" class="underline hover:text-foreground">complete side effects guide</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What is the strongest nicotine pouch?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            The strongest nicotine pouches available reach <strong>50 mg per pouch</strong>
            (Rabbit Extreme and Siberia). Other ultra-strong brands include CUBA (up to 43 mg),
            ICEBERG (40 mg), and Garant (38 mg). These are strictly for experienced users with
            high tolerance. See our full
            <a href="/blog/strongest-nicotine-pouches" class="underline hover:text-foreground">strongest nicotine pouches ranking</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What's the best nicotine pouch for beginners?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We recommend starting with <strong>ZYN Mini (1.5-3 mg)</strong> or
            <strong>HELWIT (3.5 mg)</strong> — both offer gentle strengths in comfortable
            formats. Mint is the safest flavour bet for first-timers. Read our full
            <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-for-beginners" class="underline hover:text-foreground">beginners guide</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What's the difference between mini and slim pouches?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Mini pouches</strong> are smaller, more discreet, and deliver a shorter
            experience (~20 min). <strong>Slim pouches</strong> are longer and thinner, sit
            comfortably under the lip, and last longer (~30-40 min) with more flavour. Most
            brands offer both — slim is the most popular format for daily use.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Can nicotine pouches help me quit smoking?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Many people use nicotine pouches as a tobacco-free alternative when transitioning
            away from cigarettes. They provide nicotine without smoke, tar, or combustion. While
            we can't make medical claims, the approach works for many of our customers. See our
            <a href="/blog/switching-from-cigarettes-to-nicotine-pouches" class="underline hover:text-foreground">switching from cigarettes guide</a>
            for a practical week-by-week plan.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Do nicotine pouches expire?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Yes. Most nicotine pouches have a shelf life of <strong>12-18 months</strong> from
            manufacture. The expiry date is printed on the bottom of the can. Store them in a
            cool, dry place — unlike snus, they don't need refrigeration. Expired pouches lose
            flavour and potency but aren't dangerous.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How many pouches can I use per day?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            This varies by person and strength. Most regular users consume <strong>5-15 pouches
            per day</strong>. There's no official limit, but listen to your body — if you
            experience nausea, hiccups, or dizziness, you may be using too many or too high a
            strength. Start low and find your personal rhythm.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What is the most popular nicotine pouch brand?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <strong><a href="/brands/zyn" class="underline hover:text-foreground">ZYN</a></strong>
            is the world's best-selling nicotine pouch brand, holding over 60% market share in
            the US. In Europe,
            <strong><a href="/brands/velo" class="underline hover:text-foreground">VELO</a></strong>
            (by BAT) is the leading competitor. Both are Swedish-heritage brands with 50+
            products each. Read our
            <a href="/blog/zyn-vs-velo" class="underline hover:text-foreground">ZYN vs VELO comparison</a>.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Are nicotine pouches legal in Europe?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Yes. Tobacco-free nicotine pouches are <strong>legal across the EU</strong>. They
            are not classified as tobacco products since they contain no tobacco leaf. Regulations
            vary by country — some nations have specific nicotine limits or labelling requirements.
            Age restrictions (18+) apply in all markets.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Ordering & Shipping -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Ordering &amp; Shipping</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Where do you ship?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We ship to most EU countries. Shipping availability and delivery times vary by
            destination. During checkout you will see the available shipping options and
            estimated delivery dates for your address.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How much does shipping cost?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Orders over &euro;{tenant.freeShippingThreshold} qualify for free standard
            shipping. Below that threshold, a flat-rate shipping fee applies and is shown
            at checkout before you pay.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How long does delivery take?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We dispatch orders the same or next business day. Standard delivery within
            the EU typically takes 2-5 business days. You will receive a tracking link by
            email once your order is shipped.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Can I track my order?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Yes. Once your order ships, we send a tracking link to the email address you
            used at checkout. You can also view order status by logging into your account.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What payment methods do you accept?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We accept major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard), as well as popular
            EU payment methods available through our payment provider. All transactions are
            processed securely via encrypted checkout.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Returns & Refunds -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Returns &amp; Refunds</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What is your return policy?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Due to the nature of nicotine products, we cannot accept returns on opened
            items. If you receive a damaged or incorrect product, contact us within 14 days
            of delivery and we will arrange a replacement or refund.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            My order arrived damaged. What do I do?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Email <a href="mailto:{tenant.supportEmail}" class="underline hover:text-foreground">{tenant.supportEmail}</a> with
            your order number and a photo of the damage. We will resolve the issue as
            quickly as possible, usually within one business day.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Age Verification -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Age Verification</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Why do you verify my age?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Nicotine products are intended for adults only. EU regulations require us to
            verify that all customers meet the minimum legal age in their country of
            residence before completing a purchase. This protects minors and ensures
            compliance with local laws.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            What is the minimum age to purchase?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            The minimum age is 18 in most EU countries. Some countries may set a higher
            threshold. You must confirm that you meet the legal age requirement in your
            country when placing an order.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Account & Rewards -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Account &amp; Rewards</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            Do I need an account to order?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            No — you can check out as a guest. However, creating a free account lets you
            track orders, earn loyalty points, leave reviews, and access members-only deals.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-6 py-4 font-medium text-foreground flex items-center justify-between">
            How does {tenant.loyaltyProgramName} work?
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-muted-foreground">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Every purchase earns points. You can also earn points by writing reviews,
            completing quests, and participating in the community. Points can be redeemed
            for discounts on future orders. Check your account dashboard for your current
            balance and available rewards.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

